@garga @bdrewery @swills I opened a code review that splits off git-svn, git-p4, and git-cvs as subports that depend on git (so they can be installed on top of each other). Not brilliant, but works. Would like to see the same with git-gui, so this could be installed optionally as well, but this first step might help to reduce Bryan's frustration.

